--- README.md ---
# Lab Technician Landing Page

Minimal, production-ready landing page for a lab technician. Single HTML page served by Express with plain CSS and JS. Palette: red/black/white.

## Requirements implemented
- Express server serving static assets from /public
- Health endpoint at /health returning "ok"
- Responsive layout with hero, services list, and contact form
- Plain CSS/JS (no frontend frameworks)
- Jest tests for hero title and /health endpoint

## Getting started
1. Install dependencies:
   npm install

2. Start in development (auto-restart):
   npm run dev
   # Visit http://localhost:3000

3. Start in production mode:
   npm start
   # Visit http://localhost:3000

4. Run tests:
   npm test

## Project structure
- server.js — Express server
- public/
  - index.html — Single page with hero, services, contact form
  - styles.css — Red/black/white responsive styles
  - app.js — Client-side behavior (form handling)
- tests/ — Jest tests (server and DOM)


